org.iocaste.documents.common

Class ComplexModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.iocaste.documents.common.ComplexModel
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<ComplexModel>

    public class ComplexModel
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<ComplexModel>

    Specifies a contract to instantiate a ComplexDocument.

    ComplexModel is organized in a header and one or several items groups.

    The structure of a ComplexModel is documented below:

    ComplexModel
    - header (DocumentModel)
    - items groups
    -- group 1 (DocumentModel 1)
    -- group 2 (DocumentModel 2)
    -- ...
    -- group n (DocumentModel n)

    Author:
    francisco.prates
